        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "奈莉德不知道自己是怎么说出口的。她像逃似地躲进了房间里，脸烫得头晕脑胀。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她冲进淋浴间，冷水哗啦啦地浇在头顶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "冻得一激灵，但心头那股无法形容的感受也只被压下了几分而已。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她靠着墙慢慢坐下。亲吻的触感攥住了心，直到现在都揪住不放。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她看着镜子——身上的衣服都淋透了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "水沿着红透的脸，像打了蜡的苹果和水彩画。她实在是不太认识镜子里的那个人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "冷水还浇着她。她觉得很舒服，这样还能够保持思考。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（怎么变成这样子的？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "记不清是什么时候，心被打开了一个口子，又被占据了仅有的位置。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从唯一认同的人，再到唯一相信的人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（就是那个时候，产生了这种情绪吧。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（喜欢……奇妙的情绪。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可以哭，可以笑，什么都可以做——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "听到这样温柔的话的时候，连被填满了都不自觉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她拧上水龙头，站起身，看着镜子里的自己。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "盯着微微发肿的嘴唇，又想起了刚刚的旖旎。她出了神。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "比起她的初吻，和playername在落日前的那次……刚刚的吻总算清晰了些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她有些后悔——初吻太草率，甚至没能表达自己的心意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "更像是猎人标记了猎物，或者说是野性的本能。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "心里开始期许着——应该有更好的、更完美的吻，就像刚刚那个吻一样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这更让她苦恼了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……喜欢、爱，她着实不擅长这些。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她擦干了身子，回到床上，关上了灯。房间被夜幕笼罩，她欣赏着置身黑暗的心情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在这种静谧的寂寞中，她沉沉睡去了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "敲门之前，我不自觉地想起昨天的情景。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "与以前的她不同。那时的她像是高山的雪，捧在手心沁着凉意，慢慢化成一层浅浅的水渍。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而昨天的她却像是一潭无波的水。掬起一捧，镜子般的湖面漾起层层波纹，叠在心里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "奈莉德，是我。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "门里传来一阵杂乱的声音。不一会儿，奈莉德打开了门。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "脸怎么这么红？不舒服吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Mo_girl021_happy01_052",
        "zh_CN": "……在想事情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "请进来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "今天没有出勤任务吧？有什么计划吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有。就是在房间里待着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "电脑开着。以我的视力，刚好能看清屏幕上的内容——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "《美学》论爱情篇：爱情的概念",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "《论爱》：关于爱的一些可能的结论",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（一些哲学中对爱情的分析和论述……）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有一些疑惑，所以查了一些文献。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "得出什么答案了吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有些学派认为可以使用哲学指导科学。别的方法得不出结论，我就试了试这个方法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是社会关系的分支内容，在卫城学院也是选修课，我还没有涉猎过。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以进度不理想。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（怎么有点别扭？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对恋爱感到疑惑，这确实是个暧昧、尴尬、令人害羞的话题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "应该是因为害羞，所以她避开了“为什么会疑惑”和“对哪里疑惑”这个话题。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但在回话时，却好像在进行学术讨论时那样认真。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（因为不理解这种情绪？）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "坦白说，我也感到有点不自在。光是站在她面前，就会凭空产生很多想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想要了解她更多。想让她了解自己更多。想看到关于她的更多的可能性。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想要完完整整地表达内心的情感。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如此看来，昨天的回应完全不够。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "思忖着。奈莉德则看着我，并没有因为我突然陷入沉思而有什么反应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "（……心动不如行动。）",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不好意思，走神了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "既然你也没什么事情，不如把今天交给我吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "奈莉德病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "好。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那我一个小时之后来找你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这是我们的第一次约会。虽然不可能出什么意外，但还是感到有点紧张。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在约会前的一个小时里，不止一次产生了“时间怎么不过得快点”的想法。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "天气正好，想去的餐厅也订到了位置。想说的话翻来覆去酝酿着，思考着说出的时机。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但当我再一次站在她面前的时候，那些繁杂的思绪都消失不见了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我牵起她的手，心中只剩下一个想法——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一定会是美好的一天。我保证。",
        "disable": 0
    }
